Dragos:
Upon booting up the internal systems. Dragos Begins to run a self system diagnostics. After the Diagnostics reads fine he begins to slowly boot up the rest of his systems. One at a time. Until he is fully operational. "I need to find out where I am right now and what in Cybertrons worst Crash had happen here." Dragos begins to look around to see what is going on around him.
